@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOjEsInVzZXJJZCI6ImFkbWluIiwidG9rZW5WZXIiOjQsImlhdCI6MTc3MjYyNjQyNSwiZXhwIjoxNzczMjMxMjI1fQ.BIn4y1t97fSb1S938HhmFGj4sZEC48eel_BtAsrV_p0
@recorderSeq = 1
@recPresetSeq = 1

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 1. 녹화기 CRUD
### ──────────────────────────────────────

### 1-1. 녹화기 목록 조회 (기본) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-2. 녹화기 목록 조회 (페이징) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-3. 녹화기 목록 조회 (건물 필터) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders?buildingSeq=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-4. 녹화기 목록 조회 (상태 필터) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders?status=ONLINE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-5. 녹화기 목록 조회 (통합검색) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders?search=101
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-6. 녹화기 목록 조회 (복합 필터) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders?buildingSeq=1&status=ONLINE&search=녹화기&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-7. 녹화기 상세 조회 → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-8. 녹화기 상세 조회 (존재하지 않는 ID) → 404
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 1-9. 토큰 없이 조회 → 401
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders

### 1-10. 녹화기 등록 → 201
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceSeq": 1,
  "recorderName": "101호 녹화기",
  "recorderIp": "192.168.1.101",
  "recorderPort": 80,
  "recorderProtocol": "HTTP",
  "recorderUsername": "admin",
  "recorderPassword": "password123",
  "recorderModel": "SONY SRG-X120",
  "recorderOrder": 1,
  "assignedUsers": [
    { "tuSeq": 5, "isDefault": "Y" },
    { "tuSeq": 8, "isDefault": "N" }
  ]
}

### 1-11. 녹화기 등록 (이미 녹화기 있는 공간) → 409
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spaceSeq": 1,
  "recorderName": "중복 녹화기",
  "recorderIp": "192.168.1.200"
}

### 1-12. 녹화기 수정 → 200
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recorderName": "101호 녹화기 (교체)",
  "recorderIp": "192.168.1.201",
  "recorderModel": "SONY SRG-X400",
  "assignedUsers": [
    { "tuSeq": 5, "isDefault": "Y" },
    { "tuSeq": 12, "isDefault": "N" }
  ]
}

### 1-13. 녹화기 삭제 (소프트 삭제) → 200
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 2. 녹화기 제어
### ──────────────────────────────────────

### 2-1. PTZ 명령 전송 (move) → 200
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/control/ptz
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "move",
  "pan": 10.0,
  "tilt": -5.0,
  "zoom": 0
}

### 2-2. PTZ 명령 전송 (stop) → 200
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/control/ptz
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "stop"
}

### 2-3. PTZ 명령 전송 (home) → 200
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/control/ptz
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "home"
}

### 2-4. 녹화 시작 → 200
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/control/record/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionTitle": "데이터구조론 3주차",
  "recPresetSeq": 1
}

### 2-5. 녹화 시작 (프리셋 없이) → 200
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/control/record/start
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sessionTitle": "알고리즘 5주차"
}

### 2-6. 녹화 종료 → 200
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/control/record/stop
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2-7. 프리셋 적용 → 200
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/control/preset/{{recPresetSeq}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2-8. 녹화기 실시간 상태 조회 → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/control/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 3. 프리셋 관리
### ──────────────────────────────────────

### 3-1. 프리셋 목록 조회 → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/presets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3-2. 프리셋 등록 → 201
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/presets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "presetName": "칠판 중심",
  "presetNumber": 1,
  "panValue": 0.0,
  "tiltValue": -15.0,
  "zoomValue": 2.0,
  "presetDescription": "칠판을 중심으로 촬영",
  "presetOrder": 1
}

### 3-3. 프리셋 등록 (두 번째) → 201
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/presets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "presetName": "강단 전체",
  "presetNumber": 2,
  "panValue": 0.0,
  "tiltValue": 0.0,
  "zoomValue": 1.0,
  "presetDescription": "강단 전체 와이드 뷰",
  "presetOrder": 2
}

### 3-4. 프리셋 수정 → 200
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/presets/{{recPresetSeq}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "presetName": "칠판 클로즈업",
  "zoomValue": 3.5,
  "presetDescription": "칠판 클로즈업 뷰로 변경"
}

### 3-5. 프리셋 삭제 → 200
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/presets/{{recPresetSeq}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ──────────────────────────────────────
### 4. 녹화기 로그
### ──────────────────────────────────────

### 4-1. 로그 조회 (기본) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4-2. 로그 조회 (페이징) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/logs?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4-3. 로그 조회 (유형 필터) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/logs?logType=PTZ
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4-4. 로그 조회 (결과 필터) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/logs?resultStatus=FAIL
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4-5. 로그 조회 (날짜 범위) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/logs?startDate=2026-02-01&endDate=2026-02-28
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4-6. 로그 조회 (복합 필터) → 200
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/recorders/{{recorderSeq}}/logs?logType=REC_START&resultStatus=SUCCESS&page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
